name: Cubensis
description:
4 of 4 Mushroom Plants series 

Cubensis Mushroom is a poisonous mushroom that can cause hallucinations, either visual or auditory. This mushroom can only grow to a maximum of 50 cm. New symptoms will appear 2-3 hours after consuming it. If left unchecked, you will be carried away by this mushroom to another world that you have not encountered before
